quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  56,39,"Seg imenza, deg aĂźas idsen"
  56,40,"Seg ineggura, deg aĂźas idsen"
  56,41,"At uzelmav, at uzelmav, d acu ten"
  56,42,"Deg wavu, akked waman iĂŽ$an"
  56,43,Tili n wabbu iĂŽ$an
  56,44,"Ur degs tasmuvi, lekyasa"
  56,45,"Ih, nitni zik, llan ĂŽwan"
  56,46,Zgan deg ubekkav abarar
  56,47,"Llan qqaĂŽen: \"ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, akked i$san, day a d a$ d rren"
  56,48,Akked imezwura nne$ imenza
  56,49,"Ini: \"ih, imezwura akked ineggura"
  56,50,ad ppujemmlen ar temlilit n wass ipwassnen
  56,51,"D$a, ih, a yim$eĂŽĂŽqen, i illan d inekkaĂŽen"
  56,52,"a ppeĂ§Ă§em, war ccekk, si ttejĂŽa n Zaqqum"
  56,53,A ppacaĂŽem segs ifwaden
  56,54,"Sinna, a ppernum tissit seg waman iĂŽ$an"
  56,55,A ppetessem tissit ile$wman
  56,56,"D wagi ar asen d irsen, ass uqeĂźĂźi"
  56,57,D Nekwni ikwen Ixelqen. Lemmer a ppamnem
  56,58,Twalam l$ella id iteff$en segwen
  56,59,"D kunwi ip ixelqen, ne$ d Nekwni ay d ixellaqen"
  56,60,Nseyya tameppant garawen. Ur aÂŁ izeggwir yiwen
  56,61,"iwakken a Nerr deg umkan nnwen wid i kwen icban; u kunwi, a kwen Nexleq d ayen ur tessinem"
  56,62,"Ni$ tesnem axlaq amenzu, lemmer tesmektayem"
  56,63,Twalam ayen tkerrzem
  56,64,"D kunwi i t ikerzen, ne$ d Nekwni ay d imekrazen"
  56,65,"Ma ihwa yaÂŁ, a t Nerr d uĂȘvim, d$a a kwen tekkat lwehma"
  56,66,Aql a$ nepwalas
  56,67,"Sennig waya: aql a$ neppuĂȘeĂŽĂŽem"
  56,68,Twalam aman i teppessem
  56,69,"D kunwi iten id isse$layen seg usigna, ne$ d Nekwni"
  56,70,"Ma ihwa yaÂŁ, a ten Nerr d imeĂŽ$anen. A lemmer tesnemmiren"
  56,71,Twalam times i tesskarem s uĂȘukku
  56,72,"D kunwi i s d ixelqen ttjuĂŽ is, ne$ d Nekwni ay d Ixellaqen"
  56,73,"D Nekwni i p Irran d asmekti, u d lĂąafia i wid ineĂȘwwaoen"
  56,74,"SbuccaĂą, s ccekĂŽan, isem n Mass ik, AmeqwĂŽaĂȘan"